OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Girls excluded
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas Afghan secondary schools
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freopen                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have excluded girls from   
OL,6, Afghan secondary schools, after they   
OL,7, ordered only boys and male teachers to 
OL,8, return to the classroom.               
OL,10,FSchoolgirls told the BBC they were     
OL,11,Fdevastated not to be returning.        
OL,12,F"Everything looks very dark," one said.
OL,14,FA Taliban spokesman said there were    
OL,15,Fplans to open girls' schools soon.     
OL,17,FBut there are fears Afghanistan is     
OL,18,Freturning to the harsh rule of the     
OL,19,F1990s when a similar ban on girls'     
OL,20,Fschooling was in place.                
